  37,80,Ko non woni ko Men warjorta mo∆¥∆¥im…ìe …ìen
  37,81,"Kanko, ko o jeyanoo…óo e jeyaa…ìe Amen gom…óim…ìe …ìen"
  37,82,Refti Men yooli heddii …ìe …ìen
  37,83,"Hino jeyanoo e jokku…ìe mo …ìen, Ibraahiima"
  37,84,"Tuma nde ardunoo ka Joomi makko, e …ìernde hisunde"
  37,85,"Nde o maakannoo ben makko e yim…ìe mun …ìen: \"Ko hon…óum rewoton"
  37,86,"E ko rewetee…ói fefindaa…ói, ko wanaa Alla, faala…óon"
  37,87,Ko sikku…óon e Joomiraawo tageefo ngon
  37,88,O ndaariri ndaarande ka koode
  37,89,"o maaki: \"Ko mi nawnu…óo"
  37,90,"∆Åe acci mo, …ìe hucciti"
  37,91,"O moltii e rewetee…ói ma…ì…ìe …óin, o maaki: \"E on √±aamataa"
  37,92,"Ko he…ìi on, on wowlataa"
  37,93,"O moltorani …ói, piyirgol …ói √±aamo ngon"
  37,94,"∆Åe fewri ka makko, hi…ìe yaawno"
  37,95,"O maaki: \"E on reway kon ko lesu…óon"
  37,96,"hara le ko Alla tagi on, e kon ko golloton"
  37,97,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Mahanee mo maadi, bugo…óon mo ka dul…ìayange"
  37,98,∆Åe faandanii mo feere; kono Men wa…ói …ìe sooyube …ìen
  37,99,"O maaki: \"Min on, ko mi feroowo ka Joomi am, aray nde O fewnata lam"
  37,100,"Joomi am, ye…óam ge…ìal mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe"
  37,101,"Men wewliniri mo, ge…óal mu√±√±ii…óo"
  37,102,"Nde on yottinoo e makko jahal, [Ibraahiima] maaki: \"Ko an …ìi…ó…óo am, min mi yi'ii e …óoyngol, wonnde mi…óo hirse. Ndaaru ko yi'u…óaa\". [Ismaa'iila] maaki: \"Ko onon yo baaba'en, wa…óee ko yamira…óon kon, on tawoyay lam, si Alla ja…ìii, jeyaa…óo e mu√±ii…ìe …ìen"
